      "html": "<p>\"被任命的人\"，1768年，源自法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">appointé</i>，来自 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">apointer</i> \"安排，解决，放置\"； 参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of appoint \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/appoint\">appoint</a> 和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ee \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ee\">-ee</a>。</p>"
